{"tid":363730,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"34C秦芷瑤願為梁朝偉露點","createTime":"2017-08-18T00:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T06:11:52.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":212,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4df0b8633af9ed811727a3d3bac621715ada7770","tid":363730,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T00:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170818/photo/bkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170818053924\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170818%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170818053924&h=f9edf1f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n秦芷瑤曾參選港姐。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170818/photo/bkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170818053924\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170818%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170818053924&h=a1f358dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n皮膚白滑！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170818/photo/bkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170818053924\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170818%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170818053924&h=20d63dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n笑容都幾甜美～<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170818/photo/bkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_04b.jpg?20170818053924\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170818%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20170818053924&h=11ce0a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢話最鍾意偉仔。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170818/photo/bkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_05b.jpg?20170818053924\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170818%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20170818053924&h=90eb6faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趙又廷都係佢杯茶。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170818/photo/bkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_06b.jpg?20170818053924\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170818%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20170818053924&h=c8f5c682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又話如果可以同佢哋拍戲的話。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170818/photo/bkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_07b.jpg?20170818053924\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170818%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20170818053924&h=49d0a3a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n願為藝術犧牲。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170818/photo/bkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_08b.jpg?20170818053924\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170818%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20170818053924&h=aac5a86c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n秦芷瑤有意向打女發展。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170818/photo/bkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_09b.jpg?20170818053924\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170818%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_09b.jpg%3F20170818053924&h=2be0cd4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n秦芷瑤<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170818/photo/bkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_10b.jpg?20170818053924\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170818%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001_10b.jpg%3F20170818053924&h=dd4304dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁朝偉（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n曾參選港姐的秦芷瑤（Rose），曾演過多套網絡電影，擁有34C上圍的她被問到性感底線時，她表示着泳衣冇問題，若要露點笑言要視乎劇本及對手是誰：「係梁朝偉我就會考慮吓！佢有演技，拍《色，戒》都唔會令人覺得似三級片。我又鍾意趙又廷，佢好靚仔、Man Man哋又陽光，如果佢都肯為藝術犧牲，咁我都唔怕拍！」<br />\n<br />\n之前Rose曾在內地拍攝武打片，希望能繼續挑戰做打女：「雖然都有啲戰績同受傷，但好好玩。（唔錫身？）顧唔到咁多啦，就住就會NG好多次，我直情叫對方落力啲打我，唔係我會受更多傷！」<br />\n<br />\nProfile：<br />\n姓名：秦芷瑤（Rose）<br />\n身高：1米66<br />\n三圍：34C、24、34<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170818/bkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170818%2Fbkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001.html&d=sG%2F3FYmKfJ8rriiEDeMittU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=41e1b1c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170818/bkn-20170818000021404-0818_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3adb497cc5ad147626a6f36c876008b7fa7c5d72","tid":363730,"uid":66943,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T00:12:31.000Z","msg":"二奶款"},{"pid":"8d1f0f4e45d32889d731c5dd2a61ca549f3d04d8","tid":363730,"uid":39710,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T00:16:34.000Z","msg":"大陸樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f238ddbe9867199087e10b4a50844ae1b11a0f3","tid":363730,"uid":62646,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T00:18:05.000Z","msg":"老雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbceadb1796451726b9c538f7972d38502207a2c","tid":363730,"uid":25002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T00:21:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f73c7f458c47550fedb68eef0fb179f80214729c","tid":363730,"uid":96877,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T00:25:51.000Z","msg":"滴汗想點<br />\n笑死"},{"pid":"b01b5af409ef5eb8a77bf79d6672555164e55e52","tid":363730,"uid":36390,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T00:28:36.000Z","msg":"老鷄"},{"pid":"40e351478bf69b550327f22df